titles.title: Electing Members to certain standing committees of the House of Representatives.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 1/23/2007--Passed House without amendment. (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Elects specified Members to the House Committees on: (1) Financial Services; (2) the Judiciary; (3) Science and Technology; and (4) Small Business.
